## Strategic Context Input (Regional E2E Step 4)

When invoked as **Step 4** in Regional E2E (after Steps 1-3 strategy review):
- Read `research/[REGION]/strategy-context-[YYYY-MM-DD]-[MISSION-ID].md` (from Step 1)
